General.Name: Kingston Resources Ltd
General.Description: Kingston Resources Limited engages in the exploration and evaluation of mineral properties in Australia. The company's projects include the Misima Gold project located in the Solomon Sea and Mineral Hill Mine project located in New South Wales. Kingston Resources Limited was incorporated in 1985 and is based in North Sydney, Australia.
